-- out/todo.txt --
v3 uses structure sharing (~) for issue3891.reduced.a (~(issue3891.reduced.b)) where v2 expanded the value inline. v3 reports conflicting values for issue3606.data in opposite order vs v2 (struct then string vs string then struct), with different position info. v3 shows different position info for f sub-errors. v3 shows indexElimination.inList1.x as _ instead of cycle error. v3 shows issue3597.t1 let Ok as concrete value instead of unresolved reference.
